 Letâ€™s create a GitHub-ready Ansible Project Folder Structure with Dynamic EC2 Inventory, Best Practices, and CI/CD ready format.


âœ… Ansible Project Folder Structure (Best Practice)

practicedevops-ansible/
â”œâ”€â”€ ansible.cfg
â”œâ”€â”€ inventory/
â”‚   â””â”€â”€ aws_ec2.yml              # Dynamic Inventory config (EC2 plugin)
